msgstr "本指南深入介绍了 Apache Kafka 和 SmallRye 响应式消息传递框架。如需快速入门，请参阅《 xref:kafka-getting-started.adoc[使用 Apache Kafka 开始使用 Quarkus 消息传递] 》。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/kafka.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can add the `messaging-kafka` extension to your project by running the following command in your project base directory:"
msgstr "您可以在项目根目录下运行以下命令，将 `messaging-kafka` 扩展添加到项目中："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/kafka.adoc
#, fuzzy
