#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/kafka.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "There are several other ways your application can consume incoming messages:"
msgstr "您的应用程序还可以通过以下几种其他方式处理传入的消息："

