msgstr "使用 `@Channel` 处理消息时，订阅操作由应用程序代码负责。在上例中，Quarkus REST（原 RESTEasy Reactive）端点会为您处理这一操作。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/kafka.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Following types can be injected as channels:"
